        {
            "question": "Solve: 3x - 7 = 14",
            "solution": "x = 7",
            "explanation": "3x - 7 = 14 → 3x = 14 + 7 → 3x = 21 → x = 7. Check: 3(7) - 7 = 21 - 7 = 14 ✓"
