        {
            "question": "Solve: 5(x - 2) = 15",
            "solution": "x = 5",
            "explanation": "5(x - 2) = 15 → x - 2 = 3 → x = 5. Check: 5(5 - 2) = 5(3) = 15 ✓"
        },
        {
            "question": "Solve: 2x + 3 = x + 8",
            "solution": "x = 5",
            "explanation": "2x + 3 = x + 8 → 2x - x = 8 - 3 → x = 5. Check: 2(5) + 3 = 13, 5 + 8 = 13 ✓"
